snippet.title: How Amber Heard Destroyed Her Own Career | Celebrity Craze
snippet.description:
How Amber Heard Destroyed Her Own Career | Celebrity Craze

Johnny is now getting back on his feet and winning over public opinion; after being effectively ostracized from Hollywood.

In the meantime, Amber has been losing jobs left and right. She has been kicked away from big roles. The general consensus among fans is that she orchestrated a hoax against Johnny in an attempt to ruin his career and make a financial large gain.

However, it looks like Amber’s plan has backfired and instead of ruining Johnny’s career, she’s ruining her own. Let's take a look with this video.
